WEBVTT

00:07:29.923 --> 00:07:32.548
There, I can start giving
form to each letter.

00:07:32.572 --> 00:07:34.204
I work carefully.

00:07:34.638 --> 00:07:38.733
I dedicate time to each letter
without losing sight of the whole.

00:07:39.974 --> 00:07:42.495
I draw the ends
of the letters methodically.

00:07:43.450 --> 00:07:46.098
Are they square or round?

00:07:46.986 --> 00:07:50.462
Are they pointy or plump and smooth?

00:07:52.213 --> 00:07:53.827
I always make several sketches,

00:07:53.851 --> 00:07:57.772
where I'll try different ideas
or change elements.

00:07:58.459 --> 00:08:02.906
And there comes a point when
the drawing turns into precise forms,